  <h1 class="gd-h1">Heliskiing Insurance</h1>
  <p class="gd-lede">Before you book a heli trip, sort your cover. The uncomfortable truth is that <strong>standard travel insurance often does not cover heliskiing</strong>, and even winter-sports policies frequently exclude off-piste and helicopter transport. This guide walks through what to look for, why it matters in remote terrain, and the one habit that protects you above all: <strong>read the wording and confirm the cover with your insurer</strong>. It is general information, not insurance or financial advice. When you are ready, browse <a href="/packages">the packages</a> or read up on <a href="/iceland">heliskiing in Iceland</a>.</p>
</div></section>
<section class="band band--navy gd-body"><div class="shell gd-wrap">
